@startuml
!theme plain
title Excel 批量导入：提交任务

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam ParticipantPadding 18
skinparam BoxPadding 10

skinparam participant {
  BackgroundColor #f4f4f4
  BorderColor #2c3e50
  FontStyle bold
  FontColor #2c3e50
}

skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #eef6ff
  BorderColor #2c3e50
  FontColor #2c3e50
}

skinparam queue {
  BackgroundColor #fff7e6
  BorderColor #8a5a00
  FontColor #5c3b00
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #fff8dc
  BorderColor #d4ac0d
  FontColor #333333
}

actor "Merchant" as merchant
participant "Upload API" as api #e8f4f9
participant "OSS / USS" as filestore #eef6ff
database "product_supply_task" as taskdb #eef6ff

merchant -> api: 1. 上传 Excel / 批量提交
activate api
api -> filestore: 2. 上传源文件到 OSS / USS
activate filestore
filestore --> api: input_file_ref / file_name / hash
deactivate filestore

api -> taskdb: 3. 创建 product_supply_task\nstatus=PENDING, execution_mode=ASYNC,\ninput_file_ref / file_name / input_file_hash
activate taskdb
taskdb --> api: task_id
deactivate taskdb

api --> merchant: 4. 返回 task_id
deactivate api

note right of api
提交阶段只负责保存源文件和任务元数据，
不直接解析 Excel，也不直接写正式商品表。
end note

@enduml
